name: Majestic
description: Fear of the dark future or even guessing what the future might look like has been seen since now but is still a mystery. When talking about the future, or even still around the question how will the future be? or what is the future? but what has been seen from now on is how the future supports have arrived. Such as technology that increasingly strengthens us as humans so that we can work quickly and precisely Or even more complex than that is to create an imaginative "world" created by ourselves. Which previously could only be thought of in the head but now can be made and can even be added to become more complex unlike our initial thoughts. This problem makes me experiment and implement what I have in mind about the future which has to do with time and space.
